Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.180 --> 00:00:04.080
 In this video, we will introduce Fruit Salad. 

00:00:04.080 --> 00:00:07.520
 Which is a student game Play as a group in the classroom 

00:00:07.680 --> 00:00:10.280
 For fun, excitement 

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:14.160
 And make students Get to know each other more 

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:18.520
 Teachers can play this game with children. 

00:00:18.520 --> 00:00:20.720
 Age from 8 years up 

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:25.060
 And the number of players is between 8 - 30 people 

00:00:25.060 --> 00:00:28.360
 It takes 5-30 minutes to play. 

00:00:28.460 --> 00:00:32.700
 And what you want With just a room and a chair 

00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:37.100
 Start with all students Sit in a circle 

00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:41.840
 And students with recent birthdays Standing in the middle 

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:46.780
 Then the student standing in the middle will ask the question that must be answered. 

00:00:46.780 --> 00:00:49.600
 Yes or no 

00:00:50.540 --> 00:00:54.200
 Younger children may ask 

00:00:54.540 --> 00:00:57.480
 Do you like ice cream? 

00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:01.100
 Or do you like to wake up early? 

00:01:01.100 --> 00:01:03.100
 Older players 

00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:06.180
 Often asking questions that are more personal 

00:01:06.380 --> 00:01:09.700
 For example, have you ever scented someone? 

00:01:09.940 --> 00:01:14.740
 Or have you ever done what parents do not allow? 

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:19.780
 Students who answer the question "Yes" must stand up. 

00:01:19.960 --> 00:01:24.480
 And find a new chair By which they can choose any chair 

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:27.840
 Except the chair on their right 

00:01:29.100 --> 00:01:32.000
 While everyone is looking for a new seat 

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:35.780
 The goal of the player in the middle is Sitting in an empty chair 

00:01:35.780 --> 00:01:39.140
 The players who can't find a chair Will have to stand in the middle 

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:42.480
 And asked the next question 

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:46.160
 If the player in the middle Can't think of a question 

00:01:46.160 --> 00:01:48.740
 Then shouted that Fruit Salad 

00:01:48.740 --> 00:01:53.140
 And all children must rise And go to find a new seat 

00:01:54.580 --> 00:01:59.060
 This game is easy to play, fun and students like this game. 

00:01:59.060 --> 00:02:01.240
 Because it will make each other more known 

00:02:01.240 --> 00:02:04.900
 If you are a teacher Try this game to play with kids. 

00:02:04.900 --> 00:02:09.780
 If you are a student or parent Try telling the teacher to play. 

